    smerte

    Pakke for Smerteregisteret. Lager rapporter for lokale og nasjonale data. Se også nettsida for denne R-pakken

    Installation

    You can install the released version of smerte from CRAN with:

    install.packages("smerte")

    Example

    This is a basic example which shows you how to solve a common problem:

    library(smerte)
